    "To this end, four distinct phases in this process were required: (1) selecting an appropriate force field, (2) obtaining an appropriate set of sequences for training and testing, (3) performing simulations of those sequences and (4) optimizing our deep-learning models for sequence-to-ensemble mapping.",
    "The Mpipi force field is a recently published one-bead-per-residue model for exploring sequence-to-ensemble behavior in disordered proteins 24.",
